{"tid":2338002,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】梁卓偉：疫苗主要目的為「不發病」非「不感染」 多人接種仍難做到群體免疫","createTime":"2020-12-23T16:51:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T17:23:22.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c4817b45350c61e362a53c1801c01bf21e1f0c78","tid":2338002,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T16:51:09.000Z","msg":"梁卓偉則解釋，現時的幾款「第一代」疫苗，主要目的是防止發病，防止感染的效果會較遜。他以阿斯利康疫苗作例子，提到其平均保護率是 7 成，但若細看「不感染」的保護率，只有 57 %，意味有人接種後仍然會「無症狀感染」，亦不等於不會傳染給別人，只是「保護好自己」。他提醒，不要期望「打（疫苗）到某一水平」，便能做到群體免疫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%A2%81%E5%8D%93%E5%81%89-%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E7%82%BA-%E4%B8%8D%E7%99%BC%E7%97%85-%E9%9D%9E-%E4%B8%8D%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93-%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE%E4%BB%8D%E9%9B%A3%E5%81%9A%E5%88%B0%E7%BE%A4%E9%AB%94%E5%85%8D%E7%96%AB/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%258D%2593%25E5%2581%2589-%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%25A6%2581%25E7%259B%25AE%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%2597%2585-%25E9%259D%259E-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2584%259F%25E6%259F%2593-%25E5%25A4%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E4%25BB%258D%25E9%259B%25A3%25E5%2581%259A%25E5%2588%25B0%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E9%25AB%2594%25E5%2585%258D%25E7%2596%25AB%2F&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MegMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=f49fd2cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%258D%2593%25E5%2581%2589-%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%25A6%2581%25E7%259B%25AE%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%2597%2585-%25E9%259D%259E-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2584%259F%25E6%259F%2593-%25E5%25